Step 1:
Download Arduino Software : https://www.arduino.cc/en/software

Step 2: 
Paste the URL: “https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json” into the “Additional Board Manager URLs” box 
in File->Preferences 

Step 3:
Open board manager from Tools->Board Menu, type esp32 in the search bar
Select Esp32 Dev Module


Step 4:
sudo apt install python-is-python3
pip install pyserial --user


[ESP32](esp32-pinout.png)
